Grammar

    0 $accept: Init $end

    1 Init: Global_List

    2 Global_List: Global_List Global_Statement
    3            | Global_List Option
    4            | %empty

    5 Global_Statement: Import
    6                 | IncludePath
    7                 | Namespace
    8                 | DataTypeDef SEMICOLON
    9                 | ScriptTypeDef SEMICOLON
   10                 | Data SEMICOLON
   11                 | Function
   12                 | Script
   13                 | Annotated_Script
   14                 | Class
   15                 | DataEnum SEMICOLON
   16                 | Using SEMICOLON
   17                 | AlwaysUsing SEMICOLON
   18                 | Statement_Assert SEMICOLON
   19                 | EXPECTERROR LPAREN Expression_Constant RPAREN Global_Statement

   20 Namespace: NAMESPACE Scoperes_Identifier_List LBRACE RBRACE
   21          | NAMESPACE Scoperes_Identifier_List LBRACE Namespace_Block_List RBRACE

   22 Namespace_Block_List: Namespace_Block_List Namespace_Statement
   23                     | Namespace_Block_List Option
   24                     | Namespace_Statement
   25                     | Option

   26 Namespace_Statement: Namespace
   27                    | DataTypeDef SEMICOLON
   28                    | ScriptTypeDef SEMICOLON
   29                    | Data SEMICOLON
   30                    | Function
   31                    | Script
   32                    | Annotated_Script
   33                    | Class
   34                    | DataEnum SEMICOLON
   35                    | Using SEMICOLON
   36                    | Statement_Assert SEMICOLON
   37                    | EXPECTERROR LPAREN Expression_Constant RPAREN Namespace_Statement

   38 Using: USING NAMESPACE Scoperes_Identifier_List

   39 AlwaysUsing: ALWAYS USING NAMESPACE Scoperes_Identifier_List

   40 Import: IMPORT IMPORTSTRING
   41       | HASH INCLUDE IMPORTSTRING
   42       | HASH INCLUDEIF LPAREN Expression_Constant COMMA IMPORTSTRING RPAREN

   43 IncludePath: HASH INCLUDEPATH IMPORTSTRING

   44 Option: HASH OPTION IDENTIFIER Expression_Constant ENDLINE
   45       | HASH OPTION IDENTIFIER Expression_Constant NEWLINE
   46       | HASH OPTION IDENTIFIER INHERIT ENDLINE
   47       | HASH OPTION IDENTIFIER INHERIT NEWLINE
   48       | HASH OPTION IDENTIFIER DEFAULT ENDLINE
   49       | HASH OPTION IDENTIFIER DEFAULT NEWLINE
   50       | HASH OPTION DEFAULT Expression_Constant ENDLINE
   51       | HASH OPTION DEFAULT Expression_Constant NEWLINE
   52       | HASH OPTION DEFAULT INHERIT ENDLINE
   53       | HASH OPTION DEFAULT INHERIT NEWLINE
   54       | HASH OPTION DEFAULT DEFAULT ENDLINE
   55       | HASH OPTION DEFAULT DEFAULT NEWLINE

   56 Statement_Assert: CASSERT LPAREN Expression_Constant RPAREN
   57                 | CASSERT LPAREN Expression_Constant COMMA QuotedString RPAREN

   58 DataTypeDef: StandardDataTypedef
   59            | EnumDataTypedef

   60 StandardDataTypedef: TYPEDEF DataType IDENTIFIER

   61 EnumDataTypedef: ENUM IDENTIFIER LBRACE Enum_Block RBRACE

   62 DataType: ZCONST DataType
   63         | ZAUTO
   64         | ZVOID
   65         | UNTYPED
   66         | ZBOOL
   67         | ZFLOAT
   68         | ZCHAR
   69         | ZLONG
   70         | ZRGB
   71         | BITMAP
   72         | CHEAT
   73         | COMBO
